I'm working on a mechanical shark picture. I'm in the early construction step with general design and composition. For that I generally do drawings and sketches.

I still have to work on the background, colour balance, deformations and construct the picture with pieces of photographies (I want to make it photomanip).

I think this picture is already quite fun.
